data.description: Welcome to this very well-maintained, home in Barberton! Move right into this clean and pristine 3 bedroom, 1 bath Colonial with detached 2 car garage. Nicely updated in 2018 with a spacious kitchen that features Maple cabinets, stainless steel appliances and tile backsplash. Slider leading to large, covered deck overlooking fenced-in back yard, great for children and pets and just perfect for entertaining! Nice sized bedrooms and closets. Tile floor in bathroom with step-up tub and Corian countertop. Great laundry area and plenty of storage in basement. Schedule your appointment today.
